Package com.ntu.scse

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bill
    Represents a hotel Bill object that contains the hotel room price as well as the room service orders for that room.
    BillMgr
    Represents a hotel Bill Manager that contains a list of all bills as well as methods for manipulating those bills.
    Guest
    Represents a hotel Guest, with details of the guest being stored.
    GuestMgr
    Represents a hotel Guest Manager that contains a list of all guests as well as methods for manipulating those guests.
    Main
    Represents a hotel management system for staff to use.
    Menu
    Represents one hotel Room Service Menu Item that contains information on the item.
    Order
    Represents one hotel Room Service Order that contains information on the item.
    Reservation
    Represents a hotel Reservation that contains reservation details as well as relevant room and guest details.
    ReservationMgr
    Represents a hotel Reservation Manager that contains a list of all reservations as well as methods for manipulating those reservations.
    Room
    Represents a hotel Room that contains room details.
    RoomMgr
    Represents the hotel's Room Manager that contains a list of all rooms and the methods for manipulating room facilities.
    RoomService
    Represents the hotel's Room Service that contains a list of all menus and order as well as methods for manipulating menus and order.
